		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>This heavy golden sword attacks with the power and intensity of the sun, burning nearby enemies.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Weapon</b><b>:</b> Heavy blade</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +5d6 critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>This weapon can shed bright or dim light up to 20 squares. You control the brightness and range of the light.</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power (Free Action)</b></p><p>All damage dealt by this weapon is radiant damage. Another free action returns the damage to normal.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power âœ¦ Daily (Standard Action)</b></p><p>You cause motes of light to burst out and attach to your enemies. Make an attack: Close burst 1; targets enemies; Strength vs. Reflex (apply a bonus to the attack roll equal to the weapon's enhancement bonus); on a hit, the target takes 1d8 radiant damage.</p><p>Level 14 or 19: 2d8 radiant damage.</p><p>Level 24 or 29: 3d8 radiant damage.</p>",
